(text "J302/J303 are one-to-one traces only." (at 389.89 383.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 6eed5fa3-cadd-58dc-96b2-d3c6b182e6ab))
(text "Use for power/menu/volume/brightness keypad or resistor ladder." (at 389.89 391.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a644b2fb-c2e2-5ca1-aa0a-e772618f89cf))
(text "Final pin order must follow the opened monitor's button board." (at 389.89 398.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e0dbd3bb-6303-5106-95ff-7f5399152742))
(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 480.06 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e260f68c-afd9-5fae-b44c-cb5344a4e7bc))
(text "This retained-controller path avoids external cables while preserving the Intehill controller, touch board, and speakers." (at 20.32 487.68 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a1889a14-a344-55a8-b936-9fb58662d7a4))
(text "HDMI carries display audio to the monitor's integrated speakers; no separate speaker amplifier is added in this pass." (at 20.32 495.3 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3d6487d7-463a-5cde-b1bd-854645f92d06))
(text "DDIB_TX3 is HDMI TMDS clock; DDIB_TX2/1/0 map to HDMI data2/1/0 per the Mu HDMI reference direction." (at 20.32 502.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2029db63-5223-59aa-a5c5-61b10522ff74))
(text "Keep this path HDMI 2.0/18Gbps capable end-to-end for 2560x1600@120; avoid HDMI 1.4-only cables/adapters/ESD." (at 20.32 510.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e2292300-a413-541e-bc67-c5baf667b863))
(text "U303 lets the EC gate monitor power with soft-start/current limit; set ILIM/dVdT after measuring monitor inrush/current." (at 20.32 518.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5aa7cbd2-efd0-508c-a43a-ef7186cece40))
(text "J301 is a 5V-only Type-C source with 10k Rp for 3A advertisement; add PD only if the monitor demands it." (at 20.32 525.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c4ea00de-5351-5ce9-909d-f403ad6bbef8))
(text "Mechanical choice remains open: disassembled internal HDMI/USB-C plugs, low-profile adapters, or raw-panel replacement." (at 20.32 533.4 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0cac9c7c-06e1-5a8e-bd76-68998b827747))
